==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water pitcher
<hw>Wa"ter pitch"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>A pitcher for
water.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>One of a family of plants having
pitcher-shaped leaves. The sidesaddle flower (<spn>Sarracenia
purpurea</spn>) is the type.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water plant</ent>⟦br⟧
